OL,3,CRiver Island at risk of collapse
OL,4,Cunless restructuring deal is approved
OL,6,FRiver Island is at risk of collapsing
OL,7,Finto administration within weeks if it
OL,8,Ffails to get approval for a radical
OL,9,Frestructuring plan.
OL,11,FThe high street fashion brand
OL,12,Fcurrently employs around 5,500 people.
OL,14,FThe London-based company also needs to
OL,15,Fsecure more funding for later this
OL,16,Fyear in order to preserve its future,
OL,17,Faccording to documents shared with
OL,18,Fcreditors.
