OL,3,CRiver Island at risk of collapse
OL,4,Cunless restructuring deal is approved
OL,6,FIt has laid out a major rescue plan
OL,7,Fwhich will see it shut 33 stores and
OL,8,Fpay reduced rents on a further 71
OL,9,Fshops.
OL,11,FLandlords are being asked to cut rents
OL,12,Ffor three years and potentially stop
OL,13,Fpayments completely on some sites in a
OL,14,Fbid to stem losses.
OL,16,FThe plan would need the backing of 75%
OL,17,Fof the group's creditors, who are
OL,18,Fmostly landlords, at a hearing on
OL,19,FAugust 7. It would also need court
OL,20,Fapproval.
