OL,3,CRiver Island at risk of collapse
OL,4,Cunless restructuring deal is approved
OL,6,FHowever, company documents first
OL,7,Freported by the Telegraph warned that
OL,8,Fthe chain would be "unable to pay its
OL,9,Fdebts by the end of the month" if the
OL,10,Fplan is rejected.
OL,12,FIt indicated that the company will not
OL,13,Fbe able to keep trading if it fails on
OL,14,Fthese payments and would therefore "be
OL,15,Fsubject to administration or other
OL,16,Finsolvency proceedings".
OL,18,FThe documents also highlighted that
OL,19,Fthe company faces a #10 million
OL,20,Ffunding need in September, which could
OL,21,Fballoon to #50 million by next year.
