OL,3,CRiver Island at risk of collapse
OL,4,Cunless restructuring deal is approved
OL,6,FA River Island spokeswoman said:
OL,7,F"River Island circulated its proposals
OL,8,Ffor a restructuring plan to creditors
OL,9,Fon June 20."
OL,11,F"In combination with the company's
OL,12,Fongoing transformation strategy, the
OL,13,Fplan is a proactive measure to place
OL,14,Fthe company on a firm footing.
OL,16,F"We have been having positive
OL,17,Fconversations with key stakeholders
OL,18,Fand are confident that we will achieve
OL,19,Fapproval of the plan in the next few
OL,20,Fweeks."
